      "title": "Gotabaya Rajapaksa to return",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Sri Lankan President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will return to the country from Singapore, Cabinet spokesman Bandula Gunewardena said today.",
        "Singapore has granted a 14-day short-term visit pass to former president as he entered the country on a private visit on July 14, according to immigration authorities in Singapore."
